    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2349990/extras/999eee1fc1d7f9b38469c950d6117566.avif?t=1681681717\" width=500 height=250 /></span><br><br><strong>Fateful Mages</strong> is a relaxing 2d puzzle game where you unlock characters by solving puzzles and uncovering their stories.<br>When you have discovered the extent of their past, you'll have to make a choice that seals their fate <strong>forever</strong>.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2349990/extras/de8c107a020f6c99bd2e66c9a7635015.poster.avif?t=1681681717\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2349990/extras/de8c107a020f6c99bd2e66c9a7635015.webm?t=1681681717\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2349990/extras/de8c107a020f6c99bd2e66c9a7635015.mp4?t=1681681717\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Unlock each character's backgrounds, memories, and dilemmas</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Based on the character's personality and their past, decide their fate</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>28 characters to discover </li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Dynamic puzzles of varying challenge</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Compelling stories with multiple endings</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Atmospheric soundtrack</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Can be played with just mouse</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>10 achievements to unlock (2 hidden)</li></ul><br><i>Developer's note: visuals are not necessarily final and may be subject to change in the final build of the game.</i>",
